OL,3,CFormer BNP leader could face trial
OL,4,Cover social media post
OL,6,FNick Griffin, who is from Welshpool in
OL,7,Fmid Wales, is accused of sharing a
OL,8,Fcartoon on X ` formerly known as
OL,9,FTwitter ` in 2021 that was
OL,10,F"threatening, abusive or insulting".
OL,12,FThe 66-year-old appeared at Southwark
OL,13,FCrown Court via video link on Monday,
OL,14,Fdressed in a striped shirt and black
OL,15,Ftie, alongside his solicitor Richard
OL,16,FDerby and defence lawyer Tom Edwards.
OL,18,FThe ex-Member of the European
OL,19,FParliament is being privately
OL,20,Fprosecuted by the Campaign Against
OL,21,FAntisemitism (CAA).
