OL,3,CFormer BNP leader could face trial
OL,4,Cover social media post
OL,6,FThe cartoon he allegedly shared showed
OL,7,Fa giant spider with a Star of David on
OL,8,Fits head, the CAA previously said.
OL,10,FThe former BNP leader faces two counts
OL,11,Fof stirring up racial hatred.
OL,13,FHis defence team, however, made an
OL,14,Fapplication to dismiss the charges
OL,15,Fagainst him, which will be heard at
OL,16,FSouthwark Crown Court on April 13
OL,17,F2026, the court heard on Monday.
